CATEGORIES:Health & Wellness
CATEGORIES:Emotional Wellness
CATEGORIES:Social Wellness
DESCRIPTION:Sign up here to take part in Digital Detox! This two week chal
 lenge helps guide you through managing your online life and building a be
 tter online/offline balance. You will set your own goals - maybe you want
  to reduce doom scrolling by twenty percent\, or limit use right before b
 ed. It's up to you!\nEach day\, you'll receive a mini-challenge\, and eac
 h night will include a (very) short reflection. Don't worry if you can't 
 do them all!. They're helpful guides\, not mandatory assignments. If you 
 have any questions\, or you think you might be interested but aren't sure
 \, just send a message to rjgilber@iu.edu - I'm happy to help. \n \n\nHos
 ted by: Health Promotion\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https
 ://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12100144
DTEND:20260313T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260309T020709Z
