SUMMARY:International Law Society: Center for Constitutional Democracy In
 fo Session
DESCRIPTION:ILS invites 1L members to join us for an informational sessio
 n on the Center for Constitutional Democracy (CCD). The CCD is a student 
 organization and journal that studies\, drafts\, and amends constitutions
 \, and works with governments and reformers globally. ILS and CCD members
  Anekah Fish\, Zack Zambrano\, and Griffin McKinney will speak on their e
 xperience as CCD members\, and will be available to answer questions rega
 rding application processes\, CCD work\, CCD courses\, and other relevant
  questions. Light snacks and drinks will be provided\, but feel free to b
 ring a lunch\, and come ready with questions!  For more information on th
 e CCD\, visit https://ccd.indiana.edu/ (https://ccd.indiana.edu/)&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  ILS invites 1L members to join us for a
