 y. ILS and CCD members Anekah Fish\, Zack Zambrano\, and Griffin McKinney
  will speak on their experience as CCD members\, and will be available to
  answer questions regarding application processes\, CCD work\, CCD course
 s\, and other relevant questions. Light snacks and drinks will be provide
 d\, but feel free to bring a lunch\, and come ready with questions!</p><p
 >  For more information on the CCD\, visit <a href="https://ccd.indiana.e
 du/">https://ccd.indiana.edu/</a>&#160\;</p>
