SUMMARY:Game On! Business Pathways onsite at the SRSC
DESCRIPTION:Stop by the Business Pathways table in the SRSC lobby and cha
 t with Megan Ray\, Director of Kelley Campus Partnerships.  Learn about K
 elley minors\, certificates and grad programs. Plan awesome career-buildi
 ng experiences. Discuss IU majors that can lead you into the world of bus
 iness!  Whether you're simply curious or seriously considering your next 
 move\, come ask questions and see what's possible.  A great opportunity t
 o "work out" your future!Business Pathways help you create your successfu
 l career in business.
