BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Sycamore Land Trust": "https://sycamorelandtrust.org/2026/02/little-hikers-eager-beavers/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:sycamore_land_trust
SUMMARY:Little Hikers: Eager Beavers
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260310T093000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260310T113000
UID:3bdf7f43d606a95239bb1ec03d3cee8a@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Beavers are the ecosystem engineers of nature! Join us for an 
 outdoor adventure as we explore how beavers build their dams\, shape the l
 andscape\, and create habitat for countless other species. Together we’l
 l take a short walk to observe an active beaver dam\, look for signs of be
 aver activity\, and discover what makes these busy animals so important to
  wetland ecosystems. At the end of our hike\, your Little Hikers will put 
 their knowledge to the test by building a beaver dam together!
LOCATION:Beanblossom Bottoms Nature Preserve
URL:https://sycamorelandtrust.org/2026/02/little-hikers-eager-beavers/
X-SOURCE:Sycamore Land Trust
END:VEVENT
