SUMMARY: Tattoo Design Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Find inspiration in the museum and design tattoos!\n\nHave yo
 u always wanted to design your own tattoos\, but never known where to fin
 d inspiration? Start at the museum!\n\nThis free monthly workshop provide
 s instructions for examining art to find personal meaning inside it\, and
  how to use that meaning to design tattoos based on your own life! Suppli
 es will be provided to design tattoos. Occasional guests from the local t
 attooing community may be featured to answer questions about tattoo desig
 n\, tattoo processes\, or the fascinating history of tattoos.\n\nThis gro
 up meets on the 2nd Tuesday of every month\, excluding holidays and museu
 m closures. The group will meet in the Roehm Family Art-making Studio\, l
 ocated inside the Simpson Center for Education on the 2nd floor of the Es
