DESCRIPTION:During our weekly meetings as PhotoFocus\, we host a number of
  exciting group-focused events and competitions. Among these opportunitie
 s\, we hold editing games (Edit-Offs)\, photography presentations\, crtiq
 ue nights\, movie viewings\, jeopardy competitions\, and photo exchanges 
 between members. These weekly meetings are the backbone of our organizati
 on\, and present an opportunity for the club members and leaders to socia
 lize\, grow in photographic skill\, develop editing knowledge\, and gathe
 r helpful feedback from peers. We meet for one hour per week in order to 
 maintain a regular communal atmosphere.\n\nHosted by: PhotoFocus Photogra
 phy Club\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.in
 diana.edu/event/11920046
