SUMMARY:Continuing Archives: From Past to Present (2)
DESCRIPTION:The queer community has used creative expression as a liberat
 ing act for years.  This three part program breaks the boundary of time b
 y allowing IU artists to get inspired by the past. Ending with a showcase
  on April 17th\, Continuing Archives participants will create pieces that
  resonate with their identities and passion for art history.  This will b
 e an opportunity to check in for art being made for the showcase/market! 
 You will also get the opportunity to help out with advertising the showca
 se!
