SUMMARY:A Midsummer Night's Dream
DESCRIPTION:By William Shakespeare  Directed by Samwell Rose    Star-cros
 sed lovers\, vengeful fairies\, an amateur theatre troupe. This devised p
 roduction rediscovers Shakespeare's A Midsummer Night's Dream. The play t
 akes on new meanings and relevancy for today's audiences\, exploring quee
 r joy and contemporary texts.
