DESCRIPTION:Come spend&#160\;your Thursdays at the ACC practicing your Ta
 galog and celebrating Filipino culture! Every Thursday from 4:00-5:00 PM\
 ,&#160\;we'll&#160\;host a variety of language-immersive events—(includ
 ed but not limited to) language table\, speech practice\, Tagalog tutorin
 g\, cooking workshops—to introduce the aspects that Filipino culture ha
 s to offer.&#160\;Tagalog&#160\;na&#160\;Tayo! is open to everyone\, whet
 her&#160\;you're&#160\;a beginner\, fluent speaker\, or simply curious ab
 out Filipino culture.&#160\;&#160\;All Indiana University events\, groups
 \, activities\, and&#160\;educational\, cultural\, and historical observa
 nces welcome all IU students and other members of the Indiana University 
 community.For more information\, view this event in BeInvolved (https://b
 einvolved.indiana.edu/event/11993689).
