DESCRIPTION:Week 1: Intro to Buddhism and Dharma etiquette\n\n8 Weeks Intro
 ductory to Buddhism and Meditation Course\n\nThe teachings are offered in s
 imple language and very accessible drawing the inspiration from our everyda
 y life. It will also focus on how to incorporate Buddhist teachings into ou
 r everyday lives to achieve lasting peace\, happiness\, and meaningful life
 .\n\nOne is welcome to join anytime\, as each week will be different subjec
 t. No previous knowledge of Buddhism is required. All are welcome.\n\nThis 
 course is offered Free\; donations are welcome. RSVP not required.\n\nConta
 ct Information:\nPhone: 812-334-3456\nEmail: gks@ganden.org\nWebsite: www.g
 anden.org\nFacebook: facebook.com/KhachoeShing
LAST-MODIFIED:20260131T124700Z
