 ralleled opportunity to gain hands-on professional experience and prepare
  for global careers. HLS will match you with domestic\, remote\, and inte
 rnational internships for the fall\, spring or summer!Fall applications d
 ue April 1  For more information and to apply\, visit our Internship Plac
 ement Program page: https://hls.indiana.edu/careers/internships/internshi
 p-placement-program.html (https://hls.indiana.edu/careers/internships/int
