DESCRIPTION:No need to travel far to experience Spring Break! Let your mind
 s wander and take a deep dive into some of our favorite imaginary creatures
 ! Each day\, enjoy a craft\, a scavenger hunt with a prize\, and fun conver
 sation\, planned for school-aged children. \n\nMeet us at the Switchyard Pa
 rk picnic shelter from 2-4 p.m. on March 17\, 18\, 19.\n\nAttend all three 
 days and win an extra prize!\n\nThis event is for families with young child
 ren and school-aged children. The cost is $1/participant/day\, and admissio
 n is paid only at the door. If someone offers you a ticket\, it is a scam!
