CATEGORIES:Social
DESCRIPTION:Balance at Kelley is a club focused on raising awareness for m
 ental health and being a safe and fun community for Kelley students.\nMan
 y meetings\, we start with a discussion about a mental health topic befor
 e moving into an activity that ranges from games/crafts/competitions/conv
 ersations and more. These activities are designed to help us form bonds w
 ith each other. Other meetings are designed to help you navigate being a 
 Kelley student - connecting you with resources and advice to help you wit
