SUMMARY:ACC's Student Development Workshop Series presents: "I am perfect
 ly FINE!: How do you balance productivity and self-care?"
DESCRIPTION:For this workshop\, the common myth of productivity and self-
 efficacy will be discussed to help attendees&#160\;find out how to feel g
 ood about their work and projects. Plus\, there will be a discussion (or 
 self-discussion) about finding their own definition of rest and rejuvenat
 ion. Hye Ree earned her Doctor of Psychology (Psy.D.) degree in Clinical 
 Psychology with a focus on traumatic stress psychology from Adler Univers
 ity in Chicago. Hye Ree serves&#160\;as an embedded counselor&#160\;at th
 e ACC.&#160\;All Indiana University events\, groups\, activities\, and&#1
 60\;educational\, cultural\, and historical observances welcome all IU st
 udents and other members of the Indiana University community.For more inf
 ormation\, view this event in BeInvolved (https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/
 event/12168296).
