 you.\nCome join an exciting collaboration of various organizations on\nca
 mpus\, including IU Democrats\, IU Republicans\, and more!\n\nHosted by: 
 BridgeUSA at IU\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvo
 lved.indiana.edu/event/12268838
