X-SOURCE:IU beINvolved Student Orgs
CATEGORIES:Social
DESCRIPTION:This event’s purpose is to address the generational trauma tha
 t the black community\nundergoes with the “me vs me” tactic that we tend 
 to take when it comes to mental health that\ncontinues to be passed down.
  The growth is to help manipulate and address the myth of having\nto “suc
 k it up” and not be accused of being “so angry” when we do open up. The e
 nd goal is to\nallow black students to see that they have a community on 
 campus that indeed believes and\nsupports them when it comes to mental he
 alth.\n\nHosted by: You See Me\n\nAdditional Information can be found at:
  https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11970429
DTEND:20260325T233000Z
DTSTAMP:20260309T020709Z
