 a native\, Ambassador Brewer built her career in the U.S. Foreign Service
 \, leading missions in Africa and South Asia and managing complex diploma
 tic negotiations.</p><p data-start="453" data-end="680">  If you are expl
 oring a career in the Foreign Service or international policy\, this is a
  rare opportunity for candid access. Hear how assignments are chosen\, ho
 w reputations are built\, and how leaders navigate pressure overseas.</p>
 <p data-start="682" data-end="775">  Come with real questions. Leave with
  clarity about what this path demands and what it offers.</p>
