BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"IU Bloomington Libraries": "https://events.iu.edu/libraries/event/2169097-you-probably-havent-seen-this-before"}
X-SOURCE-ID:iu_libraries
X-SOURCE:IU Bloomington Libraries
DTSTART:20260326T213000Z
DTEND:20260326T223000Z
LOCATION:Wells Library Screening Room 048
GEO:39.171006;-86.5168
SUMMARY:You (probably) Haven't Seen This Before
DESCRIPTION:Dive deep into the archival collections of IU Libraries Movin
 g Image Archive through a new monthly screening series of short films! Ea
 ch month\, rare and unique archival films will be presented focusing on u
 nderrepresented narratives and underrepresented motion-picture practices 
 that push on and expand the spectrum of what is considered "cinema."  In 
 an effort to keep audiences open-minded and with limited pre-conceptions 
 of these rare works of celluloid\, descriptions of films to be shown will
  not be shared prior to screenings. Join us based on announced themes and
  the expectation that the works you see will fall outside of Hollywood tr
 opes\, outside of mainstream commercial expectations\, and outside of con
 ventional filmmaking practices. Trust us\, you (probably) haven't seen th
 ese films before!  This program is curated by Essence London and hosted b
 y the IU Libraries Moving Image Archive Screening Room.  Please remember 
 to register below.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Dive deep into the archival collections
  of IU Libraries Moving Image Archive through a new monthly screening ser
 ies of short films! Each month\, rare and unique archival films will be p
 resented focusing on underrepresented narratives and underrepresented mot
 ion-picture practices that push on and expand the spectrum of what is con
 sidered "cinema."</p><p>  In an effort to keep audiences open-minded and 
 with limited pre-conceptions of these rare works of celluloid\, descripti
 ons of films to be shown will not be shared prior to screenings. Join us 
 based on announced themes and the expectation that the works you see will
  fall outside of Hollywood tropes\, outside of mainstream commercial expe
 ctations\, and outside of conventional filmmaking practices. Trust us\, y
 ou (probably) haven't seen these films before!</p><p>  This program is cu
 rated by <span data-olk-copy-source="MailCompose">Essence London</span> a
 nd hosted by the IU Libraries Moving Image Archive Screening Room.</p><p>
   Please remember to register below.</p>
UID:20260326T213000Z-2169097@events.iu.edu
DTSTAMP:20260113T123137Z
URL:https://events.iu.edu/libraries/event/2169097-you-probably-havent-see
 n-this-before
CATEGORIES:Performances, shows, and films
LAST-MODIFIED:20260227T153449Z
