 eativity in AI: Understanding The Known &amp\; UnknownModerator: Marcus L
 awrence (Zinstrel)    - Tom Collins (U Miami)    - Tristra Newyear Yeager
  (Music Tectonics)    - Timirah James (Artist\, AI Music researcher)    -
 &#160\; Andy West (IU Jacobs School of Music)    The summit provides an o
 pportunity to wrestle with questions about authorship\, ownership\, envir
 onmental impact\, cultural disruption\, business transformation\, and the
  meaning of creativity itself.  Primary partners for this project are the
  Maurer School of Law\, IU Innovates\, Music Tectonics\, and the AI+Digit
 al Futures Team.  AlgoRhythms is generously supported by Frank Graves\, w
