 s for Maple Syrup Day! \nHead to “The Woods” for a day of family fun as y
 ou follow the journey of maple syrup from tree to table. Enjoy free panca
 kes\, syrup harvesting stations\, a silent auction\, and more.  \n\nHoste
 d by: Bradford Woods\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://b
 einvolved.indiana.edu/event/12164485
