X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>Have you ever seen a crazy quilt? Stop by the Wyli
 e House in March to see Rebecca Wylie's 100+ year-old crazy quilt\, a bea
 utiful patchwork of fabric filled with embroidery. Then\, Saturdays March
  7 &amp\; 28\, come to our education center and learn how to stitch those
  same designs onto your own felt ornament.</p>
