X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Cicada Cinema": "https://cicadacinema.com/products/sirat-march-28-upland-wood-shop-8pm"}
X-SOURCE-ID:cicada_cinema
SUMMARY:SIRAT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T200000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260328T200000
UID:shopify-8195744432172@cicadacinema.com
DESCRIPTION:$0.00 - Tickets for the 8 PM screening of SIRAT 2025 • Morocco\, France • 115 minutes • dir. Oliver Laxe Saturday\, March 28th at Upland Wood Shop (354 W 11th St) FREE\, but ticketed | All Ages Showtime: 8pm *Sponsored by IU Arts &amp\; Humanities Council as part of Granfalloon 2026. More info at grafalloon.indiana.edu . TRAILER Synopsis : A father (Sergi López) and his son arrive at a rave deep in the mountains of southern Morocco. They are searching for Mar — daughter and sister — who vanished months ago at one of these endless\, sleepless parties. Surrounded by electronic music and a raw\, unfamiliar sense of freedom\, they hand out her photo again and again. Hope is fading\, but they push through and follow a group of ravers heading to one last party in the desert. As they venture deeper into the burning wilderness\, the journey forces them to confront their own limits.
LOCATION:Upland Wood Shop
URL:https://cicadacinema.com/products/sirat-march-28-upland-wood-shop-8pm
X-SOURCE:Cicada Cinema
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:http://cicadacinema.com/cdn/shop/files/SiratPoster2_8.5x11.png?v=1771787220
END:VEVENT
