 year round events and activities - social events\, co-ed intramural sport
 s\, Polar Plunge for Special Olympics\, supporting SKI women’s Little 500
  cycling team\, local ski/ride at Perfect North Slopes\, and trips during
  winter and spring break to real mountains!\n \n\nour website --> https:/
 /www.skiandboardatiu.com/ \ninstagram --> @skiandboardatiu\n\nHosted by: 
