DESCRIPTION:Join the Executive Advocacy Board to learn about next year's 
 Sherman Minton Moot Court Competition. This is a school-wide appellate ad
 vocacy competition that most 2Ls participate in. Executive Board members 
 and past competitors will share information about the process and benefit
 s of participation. They will also discuss other advocacy opportunities r
 un by the Moot Court Board\, including trial competitions and Alternative
  Dispute Resolution competitions.&#160\;
