 puting\, ethics\, and philosophy. Professor Nissenbaum has also contribut
 ed to privacy-enhancing free software\, such as <a href="http://trackmeno
 t.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TrackMeNot</a> (designed to prevent
  the profiling of web search histories) and <a href="https://adnauseam.io
 /" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AdNauseam</a> (designed to counter prof
 iling based on ad clicks). She holds a Ph.D. in philosophy from Stanford 
