 piness. On April 1 from 6–8 PM\, you can make your own mocktail at our DI
 Y drink bar\, or you can load up on pub‑style favorites like wings and si
 des. You can jump into trivia or take the mic on the main stage\, or you 
 can hang back and enjoy the energy of the room. And when you check in\, y
 ou’ll get a Bowling and Billiards voucher to play bowling\, participate i
