SUMMARY:Lotus Blossoms World Bazaar
DESCRIPTION:Saturday April 4th\, 2026\n11a.m. – 3p.m.\nFairview Elementary School\n\nGet ready to travel the world—no passport required!\nThe Lotus Blossoms World Bazaar is a FREE\, all-ages celebration packed with art\, music\, and discovery. With 25+ hands-on activities\, kids and families can learn to play instruments\, write their names in different languages\, explore global traditions\, and uncover the rhythm of the world. \nBring your friends and family and experience the joy of the world together at Fairview Elementary School!
URL:https://www.lotusfest.org/event/lotus-blossoms-world-bazaar/
