DESCRIPTION:<h2><b>Mad Paws Doggie Egg Hunt</b></h2><h3><b>Saturday\, April
  4 from 1-3 p.m.<br>Switchyard Park Dog Park<br>$7/dog</b></h3><p>Dogs foll
 ow their noses to a special treat-filled egg hunt at Switchyard Park! </p><
 p>Visit sponsor booths and enter to win a dog-themed prize basket. Canine c
 ostumes welcome! During the hunt\, all dogs must remain on leashes less tha
 n 6' long. </p><p>Connect with local businesses that have products and serv
 ices just for dogs and their people\, and register to win a dog-themed door
  prize basket!</p><p>All well-behaved dogs\, attached to their owners with 
 leashes no longer than six feet\, are welcome. All dog park rules apply\; <
 a href="https://switchyardpark.com/recreation/dog-park/"><u>see the list of
  all dog park rules.</u></a></p><p>For information about the Mad Paws Doggi
 e Egg Hunt\, <a href="mailto:reamw@bloomington.in.gov"><u>send an email to 
 event coordinator Bill Ream</u></a> or <a><u>call 812-349-3748</u></a>.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20251201T185245Z
