SUMMARY:The Player | City Lights Film Series
DESCRIPTION:A classic of Hollywood satires\, The Player follows film prod
 ucer Griffin Mills (Tim Robbins) through a story of blackmail\, murder\, 
 and moral decay. After he starts receiving death threat postcards from a 
 mysterious screenwriter\, Mills sets out to uncover the sender's identity
  while scheming to secure his job. [124 min\; comedy\, drama\; English]
