 tory of blackmail\, murder\, and moral decay. After he starts receiving d
 eath threat postcards from a mysterious screenwriter\, Mills sets out to 
 uncover the sender's identity while scheming to secure his job. [124 min\
 ; comedy\, drama\; English]</p>
