 nsactional law team invite students\, faculty\, and attorneys to an inter
 active\, condensed transactional negotiation competition—60 heart-pound
 ing minutes of positioning\, asymmetric thinking\, and collaboration. Thi
 s can't-miss event offers a glimpse of the format for the upcoming Intern
 al Transactional Competition in the fall of 2026\, and showcases Maurer's
  innovative curriculum and talent in the fastest growing sector of the le
 gal field. &#160\;</p>
