DESCRIPTION:Local News Day - A nonpartisan day of action supporting local j
 ournalism.\n\nSponsored by Automattic\, Montana Free Press\, Press Forward\
 , American Journalism Project\, Newspack\, and WordPress.com.\n\nNearly 3\,
 500 U.S. newspapers have disappeared since 2005\, leaving 1 in 4 Americans 
 with limited access to local print news. Local News Day was created by John
  S. Adams\, investigative reporter and founder of Montana Free Press\, to c
 onnect people with trusted local outlets.\n\nWays to get involved: partner 
 with Local News Day\, amplify the impact with your voice\, add your newsroo
 m to the Newsroom Locator Tool.\n\nLearn more: https://localnewsday.com
