DESCRIPTION:Join Grammy-nominated singer-songwriter Anne Wilson for the s
 econd leg of The STARS Tour presented by TPR.\, this Spring.  Come get a 
 first look at new music from her recently released album STARS\, alongsid
 e fan favorites like "Rain in the Rearview\," "Strong\," "Hey Girl\," and
  her multi-week No. 1 smash "My Jesus." Don't miss a powerful night of mu
 sic\, worship\, and a look at what's to come.
