SUMMARY: Another Round 30th Anniversary Spring Concert
DESCRIPTION:Another Round is Indiana University’s premier all-male a capp
 ella group. Established in 1996\, Another Round has entertained audiences
  in Bloomington and beyond for three decades! By pairing their rich harmo
 nies with their signature sense of humor\, Another Round puts their audie
 nces in the middle of a truly unique entertainment experience. Their chem
 istry and showmanship leave you with a feeling of hometown charm unique t
 o the group’s beloved Bloomington\, Indiana. Join us for a night of music
  you will not forget!
