  tales we tell&#160\;and the stories we share all bear our past\, present
 \, and future—across time and space.&#160\; And thus\, we meet&#160\;to
 gether\, where cuisines merge in fusion\, attire becomes fashion\, music&
 #160\;becomes memories\, and trends become traditions.&#160\;</div><br />
 <div>  &#160\;</div><br /><div>  We all possess&#160\;both ancestral wisd
 om and foresight that converge&#160\;in the present\, reminding us to lea
 rn from the past while remaining prudent in facing the future. &#160\;</d
 iv><br /><div>  &#160\;</div><br /><div>  Welcome to AsianFest 2026\, whe
 re we celebrate our shared histories and unique heritages. Through this y
 ear's theme\, Mosaic Traditions: Piecing a Common Ground\, we invite one 
 and all&#160\;to find peace on common ground.&#160\;</div><br /><div>  &#
