DESCRIPTION:Calling all savvy shoppers and student vendors!\nBYOB @ IU wel
 comes all students to showcase their businesses at our bi-monthly events\
 , currently held at Dunn Meadow or indoors in the IMU. While sellers must
  be IU students\, our events are open to the wider Bloomington community.
  You’ll find a diverse range of student-run businesses offering everythin
 g from vintage clothing and jewelry to art prints\, plants\, and crochet 
 items. Set up your table\, set your prices\, and engage with various shop
 pers.\nOur events highlight the creativity and entrepreneurial spirit of 
 our members while providing invaluable real-world experience in marketing
 \, negotiating\, and customer interaction. BYOB @ IU is more than just an
  organization—it's a movement dedicated to empowering the next generation
  of entrepreneurs\, helping them bring their ideas to life and connect wi
 th a broader audience.\nFollow us on Instagram (@byob.iu) to register for
  events and stay updated on upcoming opportunities!\n\nHosted by: Bring Y
 our Own Business\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinv
 olved.indiana.edu/event/11948219
