DTSTART:20260414T230000Z
DTEND:20260415T000000Z
LOCATION:IU CINEMA
GEO:39.168613;-86.517376
SUMMARY:Another Body w/Q&A | New Americas Cinema
DESCRIPTION:Taylor\, a college student\, searches for answers and justice
  after she discovers pornographic deepfakes of herself circulating online
 . Through candid video diaries\, synthetic media\, and 2D and 3D animatio
 n\, the film takes you into Taylor's online and offline worlds\, humanizi
 ng a vast social issue with little legal recourse in this compelling and 
 urgent story of technology run rampant. [80 min\; documentary\; English]A
  Q&amp\;A will follow the screening.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Taylor\, a college student\, searches f
 or answers and justice after she discovers pornographic deepfakes of hers
 elf circulating online. Through candid video diaries\, synthetic media\, 
 and 2D and 3D animation\, the film takes you into Taylor's online and off
 line worlds\, humanizing a vast social issue with little legal recourse i
 n this compelling and urgent story of technology run rampant. [80 min\; d
 ocumentary\; English]</p><p><i><strong>A Q&amp\;A will follow the screeni
 ng.</strong></i></p>
