DESCRIPTION:Get ready to sweat\, dance\, and have a blast! On Tuesday\, Ap
 ril 15\, 2026\, Union Board Mind & Body is teaming up with Pulse Dance Cl
 ub to bring you Move & Groove – Hip Hop Cardio Class\, a high-energy\, on
 e-hour hip hop cardio workout in Alumni Hall. Led by members of Pulse Dan
 ce Club\, this class is designed for all levels\, whether you're a season
 ed dancer or just someone who loves moving their body\, everyone is welco
 me on the dance floor. We encourage you to please RSVP before the event. 
 \nJoin us from 7:00–8:00 PM to take a break from the stress of the week\,
  let loose\, and get your heart pumping to some great music. This is the 
 perfect opportunity to step away from the books\, have some fun\, and end
  your Tuesday night on a high note. Snacks and refreshments will be provi
 ded\, so all you have to do is show up and move!\nAll Indiana University 
 events\, groups\, activities\, and educational\, cultural\, and historica
 l observances welcome all IU students and other members of the Indiana Un
 iversity community.\n\nHosted by: Indiana Memorial Union Board\, Pulse Da
 nce Club\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.in
 diana.edu/event/12314888
DTEND:20260416T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260309T020709Z
DTSTART:20260415T230000Z
LOCATION:Alumni Hall
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
