 ent run chapter of Toastmasters International. This organization has grow
 n to become a world leader in helping people become more competent and co
 mfortable in front of an audience. It now has over 350\,000 members in ne
 arly 17\,000 clubs in 143 countries\, offering a proven\, and enjoyable\,
  way to improve communication and leadership skills.\nKSB Toastmasters me
 ets Tuesdays from 8:00 - 9:00pm in Hodge Hall! Further announcements like
  room number and time-sensitive information will be provided in the Group
 Me. \n\nHosted by: Toastmasters at the Kelley School of Business\n\nAddit
 ional Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/1
 2144213
