UID:210a24e79ef4d65393097bac3b0f067d@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Arbor Day by planting a native tree! Sycamore Land T
 rust will give away more than 800 free native tree seedlings on Saturday\,
  April 25\, from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m. at Bloomingfoods East (3220 E. 3rd St.)
  and Bloomingfoods Near West (316 W. 6th St.) in Bloomington. Available sp
 ecies while supplies last include elderberry\, eastern redbud\, persimmon\
 , gray dogwood\, ninebark\, and red oak. This event is sponsored by IU Hea
 lth and co-hosted by Bloomingfoods Co-op Market. Tree seedlings were grown
  by the Indiana Department of Natural Resources. Learn more at sycamorelan
 dtrust.org/free-trees.
