DESCRIPTION:Enjoy the dawning of a new spring as we hike through Leonard Sp
 rings\, admiring the first flowering ephemerals! Lasting a very short time\
 , this group of flowers brings the first nectar to our emerging pollinators
 \, and restores the promise of a new season. We will discuss the folklore b
 ehind many of the names as we reconnect with the greening forest. Please we
 ar sturdy shoes comfortable for hiking. Participants must be able to go up 
 and down 100 stairs.\n\nAll Ages\n$5 per person in-city\, $6 per person non
 -city\nLocation: Leonard Springs\nSaturday\, April 25\n9-11 a.m.\nRegistrat
 ion closes 4/23.\n\nSPECIAL NOTE: Registration for this event is offered ON
 LY through Bloomington Parks & Recreation. "Resale" or transfer of registra
 tion is NOT accepted through third parties. If you are offered tickets to t
 his event\, it is a SCAM.\n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/events/76842883963831
 4/
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T130000Z
LOCATION:Leonard Springs Nature Park
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Spring Ephemerals Hike
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
