DESCRIPTION:🎶 One of Indiana's Best Record Shows!\n\nJoin us for the next 
 Bloomington Music Expo from 10 a.m. to 4 p.m. on Saturday\, April 25\, 2026
 \, at Switchyard Park Pavilion\, 1601 S. Rogers Street\, Bloomington\, Indi
 ana.\n\nExplore 55 tables packed with thousands of music items\, from pre-l
 oved and new LPs\, 45s\, CDs\, and cassettes to record sleeves\, posters\, 
 T-shirts\, music memorabilia\, and more.\n\nFind everything from bargain-bi
 n records to rare\, collectible gems. Expect heavy doses of classic rock\, 
 pop\, ’80s\, and metal\, plus punk\, soul\, R&B\, jazz\, hip-hop\, country\
 , bluegrass\, soundtracks\, oddities\, you name it.\n\n🕚 General admission
  opens at 10 a.m. for $2 (max $10 per family\, kids 12 & under free).\n💵 A
 dmission is cash only.\n\n🎁 Door prizes at 11 a.m. and 1 p.m.\, including 
 BCW Record Supplies and show shopping certificates!\n\n💵 Cash preferred. S
 ome dealers accept cards\, PayPal\, Venmo\, Zelle\, and more.\n\n👉 Learn m
 ore at ftrvinyl.com/bloomington-music-expo\n\n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/ev
 ents/671493955608344/
LAST-MODIFIED:20260306T130000Z
LOCATION:Switchyard Park - City of Bloomington\, IN
SEQUENCE:128
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Bloomington Music Expo Spring 2026
TRANSP:OPAQUE
