DESCRIPTION:Find resources for family wellness and fun!\n\nVisit the annual
  Children&#39\;s Expo to find Bloomington&#39\;s best resources\, services 
 and programs just for children and families! The Expo features dozens of ex
 hibitor booths\, active fun for elementary school-age children and more! Ad
 mission is free. The Expo takes place inside the Pavilion at Switchyard Par
 k. \n\nFor more information on the Children&#39\;s Expo contact Tara Brooke
  at <a href="mailto:tara.brooke@bloomington.in.gov" target="_blank">tara.br
 ooke@bloomington.in.gov</a> or 812-349-3773.\n\nThere is no admission to at
 tend this event. If someone offers you a ticket to attend or a vendor space
 \, it is a SCAM!
