SUMMARY:Soup for the Soul and Study Hours
DESCRIPTION:12pm (soup until supplies last) at La Casa  Stop by for a cup
  of soup and other treats for lunch as you wrap up the last week of class
 es. Stay as long as you need\, we're here if you need a space to study an
 d prepare for finals.  Study Hours:  Monday–Thursday: 9am–9pm  Friday
 : 9am–5pm  Coffee\, tea\, and plenty of encouragement are always availa
 ble!
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  12pm (soup until supplies last) at La C
 asa</p><p>  Stop by for a cup of soup and other treats for lunch as you w
 rap up the last week of classes. Stay as long as you need\, we're here if
  you need a space to study and prepare for finals.</p><p>  Study Hours:<b
 r />  Monday–Thursday: 9am–9pm<br />  Friday: 9am–5pm</p><p>  Coffe
 e\, tea\, and plenty of encouragement are always available!</p>
