   We will talk about:</p><ul data-start="1099" data-end="1389"><li data-s
 tart="1099" data-end="1151"><p data-start="1101" data-end="1151">      Br
 eaking into intelligence and national security    </p></li><li data-start
 ="1152" data-end="1209"><p data-start="1154" data-end="1209">      Moving
  between government\, analysis\, and policy roles    </p></li><li data-st
 art="1210" data-end="1271"><p data-start="1212" data-end="1271">      Neg
 otiation and coalition building in real-world settings    </p></li><li da
 ta-start="1272" data-end="1343"><p data-start="1274" data-end="1343">    
   The risks\, trade-offs\, and personal decisions behind public service  
   </p></li><li data-start="1344" data-end="1389"><p data-start="1346" dat
 a-end="1389">      What early-career professionals get wrong    </p></li>
 </ul><p data-start="1391" data-end="1555">  If you are serious about a fu
