SUMMARY:1776 | Screening the Semiquincentennial
DESCRIPTION:Adapted from the Tony-award winning smash hit\, 1776 follows 
 colonial representatives as they gather in Philadelphia with the aim of e
 stablishing a set of governmental rules for the burgeoning United States.
  With members of the Broadway cast reprising their roles in the film\, 17
 76 is a testament to the spirit of the country's founders. [141 min\; mus
 ical\; English]
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Adapted from the Tony-award winning sma
 sh hit\, <i>1776</i> follows colonial representatives as they gather in P
 hiladelphia with the aim of establishing a set of governmental rules for 
 the burgeoning United States. With members of the Broadway cast reprising
  their roles in the film\, <i>1776</i> is a testament to the spirit of th
 e country's founders. [141 min\; musical\; English]</p>
