SUMMARY:Spring Plant Sale to Benefit our Native Plant Nursery
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260502T090000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260502T140000
UID:06c7e4c25db9d9600de3f00ba8f5c94c@sycamorelandtrust.org
DESCRIPTION:We are thrilled to announce our fifth annual Spring Plant Sale
 ! We are offering over 40 species of plants that were homegrown in our Nat
 ive Plant Nursery from seed to plant plug. Many species are grown from loc
 ally collected seed at nearby preserves. All species are ethically sourced
  and native to southern Indiana\, providing benefits to local pollinators 
 and wildlife. Plants sell for $4 each\, with all proceeds going back into 
 nursery operations and native plant restoration projects. Stop by to learn
  from experienced staff and volunteers on the advantages of gardening with
  native species!
LOCATION:Bloomingfoods East Parking Lot
