 diana.edu/visit/your-visit.html"><span data-contrast="none">where to find
  us\, where to park\, accessibility\, and museum guidelines</span></a><sp
 an data-contrast="none">.</span></li></ul><h3><strong>About Your Facilita
 tor</strong></h3><p>  Dedaimia Whitney earned an MFA in fiction from Indi
 ana University under the direction of Scott Russell Sanders. She taught c
 reative writing at Franklin College for many years. She has served the mu
 seum as a docent since 2019. Her favorite works of art are those that are
  both visually stimulating and thought-provoking.</p>
