X-SOURCE-ID:brown_county_playhouse
X-SOURCE:Brown County Playhouse
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260819T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260819T213000
DTSTAMP:20260308T215238
CREATED:20260225T143751Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260227T135521Z
UID:10001415-1787166000-1787175000@browncountyplayhouse.org
SUMMARY:Chamberfest Brown County: Letters From The Front
DESCRIPTION:BUY TICKETS\n\nIntroducing New Music Celebrating History And Honoring Service \nLetters From The Front is a new musical work for four voices and piano. Composed by New York composer Patrick Zimmerli with libretto by Mirabelle Ordinaire\, this song cycle is based on letters sent by service members and their loved ones during wartime. Each piece is based on an actual letter written during one of our nation’s most crucial wars\, including the American Revolution\, the Civil War\, World War I\, World War II\, Vietnam\, and the Gulf War. \nThis new work will be released in the summer of 2026 to celebrate the 250th birthday of the United States. \n\n\n\n\n\nFeaturing:  \n\n\nANGELA BORN – MEZZO-SOPRANO \n\n\nDAVID GOVERTSEN – BASS-BARITONE \n\n\nDESIRÉE HASSLER – SOPRANO \n\n\nTYLER LEE – TENOR \n\n\nLAN GINDES – PIANO \n\n\nBUY TICKETS
URL:https://browncountyplayhouse.org/event/chamberfest-letters-from-the-front/
LOCATION:Brown County Playhouse\, 70 S. Van Buren St\, Nashville\, IN\, 47448\, United States
CATEGORIES:Featured Event,Live Shows,Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://browncountyplayhouse.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2026-Chamberfest_web_event.jpg
END:VEVENT
