DESCRIPTION:<p>The Board of Park Commissioners is a policy-making authority
  for the City of Bloomington Parks and Recreation Department. The Board is 
 comprised of four members appointed by the Mayor.</p><p>Statutory Authority
 : <a href="http://www.in.gov/legislative/ic/code/title36/ar10/ch4.html"><u>
 (I.C. 36-10-4) (BMC 2.20)</u></a></p><p>The Board meets at Bloomington's Ci
 ty Hall at 5 p.m. on the third Thursday of the month\, with some exceptions
  for holidays.</p><p>See meeting agendas and notes from the Board of Park C
 ommissioners online at <a href="https://bloomington.in.gov/boards/park-comm
 issioners">https://bloomington.in.gov/boards/park-commissioners</a></p><p>F
 or more information about the Board of Park Commissioners\, <a href="mailto
 :parks@bloomington.in.gov"><u>send an email to Parks and Recreation Departm
 ent Director Tim Street</u></a> or call<a><u> 812-349-3700</u></a>.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20251119T202904Z
LOCATION:City of Bloomington\, 401 N Morton St\, Bloomington\, IN 47404\, U
 SA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Board of Park Commissioners Meeting
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
